cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.SE 

The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques and automatic feature engineering methods, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also mentions the use of these techniques in tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV) and scalability in large-scale industrial tasks (cs.SE).
